SPAN></DIV>\r\n<DIV style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">Nguyễn Cao Phương Thanh, khoa Mầm non 3B - ĐH Sư phạm<o:p></o:p></SPAN></DIV>\r\n<DIV style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"></SPAN>&nbsp;</DIV>\r\n<DIV style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><IMG src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/y0V2Vnsx49nhQPv7HdH/Image/2012/11/aerobic2310128-91f50.jpg" alt="Nguyễn Hà thu Thảo, khoa Ứng dụng 1B - ĐH Nghệ thuật"></SPAN></DIV>\r\n<DIV style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">Nguyễn Hà thu Thảo, khoa Ứng dụng 1B - ĐH Nghệ thuật<o:p></o:p></SPAN></DIV>\r\n<DIV style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"></SPAN>&nbsp;</DIV>\r\n<DIV style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><IMG src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/y0V2Vnsx49nhQPv7HdH/Image/2012/11/aerobic2310129-91f50.jpg" alt="Lê Thị Hà Thu, khoa Khoa Du lịch K44"></SPAN></DIV>\r\n<DIV style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">Lê Thị Hà Thu, khoa Khoa Du lịch K44<o:p></o:p></SPAN></DIV>\r\n<DIV style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"></SPAN>&nbsp;</DIV>\r\n<DIV style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><IMG src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/y0V2Vnsx49nhQPv7HdH/Image/2012/11/aerobic23101210-91f50.jpg" alt="Bùi Huyền Trang, khoa K45C KHĐT - ĐH kinh tế"></SPAN></DIV>\r\n<